      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 1449.2963504228514,
        "height": 612.0936015224503,
        "content": "### Sub-workflow: Claim Status Google Sheet Tool\nThe AI agent calls this sub-workflow to read claim tracking data from Google Sheets.\n\nExpected sheet columns for demo:\n- row_number\n- claim_reference_number\n- client_name\n- policy_number\n- claim_status\n- current_stage\n- pending_action\n- agent_review_status\n- doctor_review_status\n- finance_handoff_status\n- last_updated\n- support_contact\n\nThe tool can list columns, fetch a column across all rows, or fetch one full claim row by row_number."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "8761e314-c1f2-4edd-88ea-bfeb02dc8f1a",
      "name": "Sticky Note2",
