        "color": 7,
        "width": 927.5,
        "height": 486.5625,
        "content": "### Main workflow: AI Claim Status Tracking Assistant\nClient asks for claim status in chat. The AI searches the Google Sheet and replies using claim tracking data only."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "e793b816-68d9-42ef-b9b0-6fe22aa375e8",
